# Audio Transcriptions API

## Endpoint
POST {{.BaseURL}}/v1/audio/transcriptions

## Description
Transcribes audio into the input language.

## Authentication
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY

## Example Request
```bash
curl {{.BaseURL}}/v1/audio/transcriptions \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -F file="@audio.mp3" \
  -F model="whisper-1"
```

## Parameters
- **file** (required): Audio file (flac, mp3, mp4, mpeg, mpga, m4a, ogg, wav, webm)
- **model** (required): Model identifier (whisper-1)
- **language**: Language of input audio (ISO-639-1 format)
